{"TIKE":[{"def":"A countryman or clown; a boorish person.","pos":""}],"TIKOR":[{"def":"A starch or arrow-root made from the tubes of an East Indian zinziberaceous plant (Curcuma angustifolia); also, the plant itself.","pos":""},{"def":"An East Indian tree (Garcinia pedunculata) having a large yellow fleshy fruit with a pleasant acid flavor.","pos":""}]}